OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHosepipe ban announced for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FKent and Sussex            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A hosepipe and sprinkler ban is being  
OL,6, imposed on people across Kent and      
OL,7, Sussex, South East Water has confirmed.
OL,9,FThe firm said it "had no choice"       
OL,10,Ffollowing the driest July on record.   
OL,12,FThe measure, which comes into force on 
OL,13,F12 August, affects at least one million
OL,14,Fpeople, and rule-breakers could be hit 
OL,15,Fwith a #1,000 fine.                    
OL,17,FIt follows pleas from the water company
OL,18,Ffor people to only use water for       
OL,19,Fessential purposes during hot weather  
OL,20,Fwarnings and shortages last month.     
